00027 Implemente_instanciable(Champ_Generique_Predefini,"Predefini",Champ_Gen_de_Champs_Gen);
00028 // XD predefini champ_generique_base predefini -1 This keyword is used to post process predefined postprocessing fields.
00029 // XD attr pb_champ deuxmots pb_champ 0 { Pb_champ nom_pb nom_champ } : nom_pb is the problem name and nom_champ is the selected field name. The available keywords for the field name are: energie_cinetique_totale, energie_cinetique_elem, viscosite_turbulente, viscous_force_x, viscous_force_y, viscous_force_z, pressure_force_x, pressure_force_y, pressure_force_z, total_force_x, total_force_y, total_force_z, viscous_force, pressure_force, total_force

00036 // -cf Champ_Gen_de_Champs_Gen::readOn
00037 // -Creation de l expression en fonction de type_champ_ qui a ete lu
00038 // -Lecture de champ_
00039 Entree& Champ_Generique_Predefini::readOn(Entree& s )
00040 {
00041   Champ_Gen_de_Champs_Gen::readOn(s);
00042   Nom expression;
00043   expression = construit_expression();
00044   Entree_complete s_complete(expression,s);
00045   s_complete>>champ_;
00046   return s ;
00047 }

00057 int Champ_Generique_Predefini::lire_motcle_non_standard(const Motcle& mot, Entree& is)
00058 {
00059   if (mot=="Pb_champ")
00060     {
00061 // Lecture du nom du probleme et du champ a construire
00062       is >> nom_pb_ >> type_champ_;
00063       return 1;
00064     }
00065   else
00066     return Champ_Generique_base::lire_motcle_non_standard(mot,is);
00067   return 1;
00068 }

00089 const Noms Champ_Generique_Predefini::get_property(const Motcle& query) const
00090 {
00091   Motcles motcles(1);
00092   motcles[0] = "unites";
00093   int rang = motcles.search(query);
00094   switch(rang)
00095     {
00096     case 0:
00097       {
00098         Noms mots(1);
00099         if (Motcle(type_champ_)=="ENERGIE_CINETIQUE_TOTALE")
00100           mots[0] = "kg.m2/s2";
00101         else if (Motcle(type_champ_)=="ENERGIE_CINETIQUE_ELEM")
00102           mots[0] = "kg/(m.s2)";
00103         else if (Motcle(type_champ_)=="VISCOSITE_TURBULENTE")
00104           mots[0] = "m2/s";
00105         else if (Motcle(type_champ_)=="VISCOUS_FORCE_X")
00106           mots[0] = "kg.m2/s";
00107         else if (Motcle(type_champ_)=="VISCOUS_FORCE_Y")
00108           mots[0] = "kg.m2/s";
00109         else if (Motcle(type_champ_)=="VISCOUS_FORCE_Z")
00110           mots[0] = "kg.m2/s";
00111         else if (Motcle(type_champ_)=="PRESSURE_FORCES_X")
00112           mots[0] = "kg.m2/s";
00113         else if (Motcle(type_champ_)=="PRESSURE_FORCES_Y")
00114           mots[0] = "kg.m2/s";
00115         else if (Motcle(type_champ_)=="PRESSURE_FORCES_Z")
00116           mots[0] = "kg.m2/s";
00117         else if (Motcle(type_champ_)=="TOTAL_FORCE_X")
00118           mots[0] = "kg.m2/s";
00119         else if (Motcle(type_champ_)=="TOTAL_FORCE_Y")
00120           mots[0] = "kg.m2/s";
00121         else if (Motcle(type_champ_)=="TOTAL_FORCE_Z")
00122           mots[0] = "kg.m2/s";
00123         else if (Motcle(type_champ_)=="VISCOUS_FORCE")
00124           mots[0] = "kg.m2/s";
00125         else if (Motcle(type_champ_)=="PRESSURE_FORCE")
00126           mots[0] = "kg.m2/s";
00127         else if (Motcle(type_champ_)=="TOTAL_FORCE")
00128           mots[0] = "kg.m2/s";
00129         return mots;
00130         break;
00131       }
00132     }
00133   return champ_->get_property(query);
